Enclosing interface:
IMonitoringRecord
public static interface IMonitoringRecord.BinaryFactory

Any record that implements this interface has to conform to certain specifications.

These records can use final fields and thus provide better performance.

  • a constructor accepting a ByteBuffer and a IRegistry as arguments possibly throwing BufferUnderflowException.
  • a public static final int SIZE specifying the binary size of the record, usually returned via IMonitoringRecord.getSize().
  • the IMonitoringRecord.initFromBytes(ByteBuffer, IRegistry) method does not have to be implemented

Since:
1.8
